recent_changes.Description: Advanced Intrusion Detection Environment - dynamic binary AIDE is an intrusion detection system that detects changes to files on the local system. It creates a database from the regular expression rules that it finds from the config file. Once this database is initialized it can be used to verify the integrity of the files.
